options.content: DASHBOARD

targets.query:
from(bucket: "btg/supan")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "t_supan_1" or r["_measurement"] == "t_supan_2" or r["_measurement"] == "t_supan_3")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      r with _measurement: 
        if r["_measurement"] == "t_supan_1" then "Temp 1" else 
        if r["_measurement"] == "t_supan_2" then "Temp 2" else 
        if r["_measurement"] == "t_supan_3" then "Temp 3" else r["_measurement"]
  }))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: last, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "last")

options.content: POWER USAGE PANEL

targets.query:
from(bucket: "btg/supan")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "pow_supan_1" or r["_measurement"] == "pow_supan_2" or r["_measurement"] == "pow_supan_3")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      r with _measurement: 
        if r["_measurement"] == "pow_supan_1" then "Power 1" else 
        if r["_measurement"] == "pow_supan_2" then "Power 2" else 
        if r["_measurement"] == "pow_supan_3" then "Power 3" else r["_measurement"]
  }))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "last")
SELECT (mean("value")  / 1000)*30*24*4 FROM "pow_supan_1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null)
SELECT (mean("value")  / 1000)*30*24*4 FROM "pow_supan_2" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null)
SELECT (mean("value")  / 1000)*30*24*4 FROM "pow_supan_3" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "pow_supan_1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null)

SELECT mean("value") FROM "pow_supan_3" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null)

options.content: ALARM PANEL

targets.query: SELECT first("value") FROM "supan_alarm_status" WHERE time >= now() - 1h AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT last("value") FROM "supan_alarm_status" WHERE topic = btg_alarm_status_supan AND "value" < 10 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
